          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-04676">To ask the Chancellor of the Exchequer how much income has been received by the Crown Estate from wind-powered electricity generating installations situated offshore for each financial year since 1997. [134333]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
